Package: dfsaneacc
Title: Accelerated Derivative-Free Method for Large-Scale Nonlinear Systems of Equations
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2023-03-30
Authors@R: c(person("Ernesto G.", "Birgin", role=c("aut", "ctb")),
