Description: Secant acceleration applied to derivative-free Spectral
  Residual Methods for solving large-scale nonlinear systems of
  equations. The main references follows: W. La Cruz, J. M. Martinez,
  and M. Raydan (2006) <doi:10.1090/S0025-5718-06-01840-0>;
  E. G. Birgin and J. M. Martinez (2022) <doi:10.1137/20M1388024>.
